            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Consentii </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Domitio Iusto <lb n="2"/>Aemiliano <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uiti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omano</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> curatori <lb n="4"/>rei publicae ob <lb n="5"/>eximium amorem <lb n="6"/>in patriam et <lb n="7"/>cives ex decreto <lb n="8"/>ordinis et suffra<lb break="no" n="9"/>giis populi civi ka<lb break="no" n="10"/>rissimo <expan><abbr>Lep</abbr><ex>citani</ex></expan> publice </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Quintii <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>aminis</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>er</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>etui</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>erdotalis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ob meritum labo<lb break="no" n="2"/>ris et legationis <lb n="3"/>perfectae <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Aemilio Quinto <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>amini</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>er</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>etuo</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>sacerdotali <lb n="6"/>ordo splendidis<lb break="no" n="7"/>simus civitatis <lb n="8"/>Lepcimagnensium <lb n="9"/>dedit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Base used three times: IRT 561 carved on the original text erased; then IRT 588 on the left side. Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 561: 3.5-5; IRT 588: 3-5. Datierung: IRT 561: tetrarchische Zeit; IRT 588: 383-388. Interpunktion: IRT 561 u. 588: Palmette. (B): AE 1950: Z. 1: Quinti fl(aminis) sac(erdotalis).</p>
            </div>
